data.name: dataGridViewTextBoxColumn5.ToolTipText
data.value: Hourly specify in Minutes to reoccur, Daily 1-31 for specific day of month and overrides the day selection Mon-Fri. Monthly, -1 to -5 Nth day of month, -1 with Monday selected yields 1st Monday of Month or -5 with Fri selected yields 5th Friday of month. Select Only one day in week. Interval Type Monthly must be selected.
